gui.model.application.scenes

Class Scene<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.model.application.scenes.Scene<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the scene (e.g. java.awt.Window)
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DialogScene, FrameScene, WebPageScene, WindowScene

    public abstract class Scene<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class representing a GUI scene. A scene can be a window, dialog, frame or a web page.
    Author:
    Michaela Bacikova, Slovakia, michaela.bacikova@tuke.sk
